1
00:00:02,860 --> 00:00:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Mobu-san's gone missing?</font>

2
00:00:05,480 --> 00:00:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, you could say that.</font>

3
00:00:08,120 --> 00:00:11,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Um, aren't you worried, ma'am?</i></font>

4
00:00:11,700 --> 00:00:12,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing new.</font>

5
00:00:13,350 --> 00:00:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moment his interest is piqued,
 he cuts off all contact.</font>

6
00:00:15,220 --> 00:00:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Where the heck did that punk go?</i></font>

7
00:00:16,360 --> 00:00:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if things get hairy, 
he can disappear for days.</font>

8
00:00:17,030 --> 00:00:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}H-How scary. So scary.</font>

9
00:00:19,170 --> 00:00:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then he comes home perfectly well,
so it feels silly worrying about him.</font>

10
00:00:24,250 --> 00:00:27,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is that so?</font>

11
00:00:27,110 --> 00:00:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll get him to contact you 
as soon as he returns.</i></font>

12
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you. I'll be waiting.</font>

13
00:00:33,370 --> 00:00:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I couldn't tell her.</i></font>

14
00:00:36,050 --> 00:00:38,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I called Mob-san and a voice said...</i></font>

15
00:00:38,310 --> 00:00:41,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is why I warned him.</i></font>

16
00:00:42,580 --> 00:00:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And it clearly wasn't his voice.</i></font>

17
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've tried calling him a few times since, 
but he's not picking up.</i></font>

18
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hope Mob-san's okay.</i></font>

19
00:00:55,930 --> 00:00:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanamugi... Hanamugi...</font>

20
00:00:59,540 --> 00:01:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, found it.</font>

21
00:01:04,010 --> 00:01:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter, Chie-sensei?</font>

22
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no, it's nothing.</font>

23
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:12,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No? Well, it's almost time, so could 
you get the kids to come back inside?</font>

24
00:01:13,180 --> 00:01:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I can do that.</font>

25
00:01:15,430 --> 00:01:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's Chie-sensei, huh? 
Just as I thought.</font>

26
00:01:19,540 --> 00:01:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan.</font>

27
00:01:21,950 --> 00:01:24,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to put things away.</font>

28
00:01:24,710 --> 00:01:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stop when I fall.</font>

29
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:29,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No fair, Kaya. You never fall.</font>

30
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hurry up and get off!</font>

31
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya. Her name uses the kanji for "God"
 and the number "eight."</font>

32
00:01:31,180 --> 00:01:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sensei! Kaya-chan's not doing what she's told!</font>

33
00:01:32,430 --> 00:01:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's time to go!</font>

34
00:01:35,310 --> 00:01:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's the eighth shrine maiden.</font>

35
00:01:38,370 --> 00:01:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

36
00:01:40,270 --> 00:01:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's a monster.</font>

37
00:01:43,830 --> 00:01:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mean? Selfish? Or just different?</i></font>

38
00:01:50,270 --> 00:01:54,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There are children who are 
seen that way by others.</i></font>

39
00:01:54,600 --> 00:02:01,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But what if that child </i>could<i> 
see something you couldn't?</i></font>

40
00:02:02,450 --> 00:02:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the story of Kaya-chan, 
a girl who could see ghosts.</i></font>

41
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:20,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

42
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:20,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

43
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

44
00:03:37,990 --> 00:03:41,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Episode 8: Reversed Isn't Scary</font></b></font></font>

45
00:03:37,990 --> 00:03:40,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font color="#444c46">Family</font></font></b></font>

46
00:03:37,990 --> 00:03:40,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="20"><font color="#4b4541">Fall
Festival</font></font></b></font>

47
00:03:37,990 --> 00:03:40,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font face="Arial"><font color="#0c1319">October 24th (Sat)</font></font></b></font>

48
