<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font face="Arial"><font color="#595d59">Central Shopping Street - Station Front Street</font></font></b></font>

49
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Impact"><font size="25"><font color="#424542">Family</font></font></font></b></font>

50
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Impact"><font size="40"><font color="#424542">Fall
Festival</font></font></font></b></font>

51
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font size="15"><font face="Arial"><font color="#393e3a">October 24th (Sat)</font></font></font></b></font>

52
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font size="15"><font face="Arial"><font color="#414e4e">Central Shopping Street - Station Front Street</font></font></font></b></font>

53
00:03:42,850 --> 00:03:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye, Sensei.</font>

54
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

55
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

56
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like it like this!</font>

57
00:03:51,090 --> 00:03:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop being difficult.</font>

58
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's okay like this! No!</font>

59
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

60
00:03:55,930 --> 00:03:57,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Sensei.</font>

61
00:03:57,480 --> 00:04:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's wearing his shoes on the wrong feet, 
and his socks are inside out.</font>

62
00:04:02,550 --> 00:04:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I tell him to fix them, he says...</font>

63
00:04:04,140 --> 00:04:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay like this!</font>

64
00:04:05,810 --> 00:04:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's not. It means you're dead.</font>

65
00:04:09,010 --> 00:04:09,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

66
00:04:10,230 --> 00:04:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long ago, to signal when someone died,
everything on them got reversed.</font>

67
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:19,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the way you're dressed now means
you died, Takkun. Are you okay with that?</font>

68
00:04:22,910 --> 00:04:25,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, for crying out loud.</font>

69
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No way!</font>

70
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Takkun, you can put 
your own socks and shoes on now?</font>

71
00:04:35,790 --> 00:04:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember how you were 
always asking for help?</font>

72
00:04:39,430 --> 00:04:40,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

73
00:04:40,670 --> 00:04:43,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've grown so much! That's incredible!</font>

74
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, I wish I'd seen you 
put them on by yourself.</font>

75
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, I know! Could you show me and 
your grandma how you put them on?</font>

76
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay!</font>

77
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're amazing, Sensei.</font>

78
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, this is nothing.</font>

79
00:05:11,450 --> 00:05:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job, Takkun.</font>

80
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:14,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

81
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye, Sensei!</font>

82
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:23,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye.</font>

83
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any word from Mob-san?</font>

84
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="11"><font color="#6d6e59">Mob Osamu</font></font></b></font>

85
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="11"><font color="#6d6e59">Voice Call</font></font></b></font>

86
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="11"><font color="#6d6e59">Mob-san</font></font></b></font>

87
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="11"><font color="#6d6e59">Did something come up?</font></font></b></font>

88
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="11"><font color="#6d6e59">Is it something related
to Kaya-chan's aunt?</font></font></b></font>

89
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="11"><font color="#6d6e59">Her name is Nana-san</font></font></b></font>

90
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="11"><font color="#6d6e59">Canceled</font></font></b></font>

91
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="11"><font color="#6d6e59">Canceled</font></font></b></font>

92
00:05:33,660 --> 00:05:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess not.</font>

93
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:39,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#703d06">Civic Park</font></b></font></font></font>

94
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="13"><font color="#3e3926">I have something important to tell you. Come alone.</font></font></b></font>

95
00:05:42,990 --> 00:05:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me?!</font>

96
00:05:50,250 --> 00:05:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He finally gets in touch out of nowhere 
and asks to meet here at this time.</font>

97
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, how long's he gonna
 make me wait?</font>

98
00:05:58,090 --> 00:06:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="16"><b>{\an8}<font color="#703d06">Civic Park</font></b></font></font></font>

99
00:05:58,090 --> 00:06:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="10"><font color="#4a4e3a">I have something important to tell you. Come alone.</font></font></b></font>

100
00:05:58,090 --> 00:06:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="13"><font color="#4a4e3a">I'm here. Where can we meet?</font></font></b></font>

101
00:05:58,090 --> 00:06:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="13"><font color="#4a4e3a">Where are you?</font></font></b></font>

102
00:05:58,420 --> 00:06:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="13"><font color="#4a4e3a">Hey</font></font></b></font>

103
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have work tomorrow, you know!</font>

104
00:06:08,050 --> 00:06:09,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's it! I'm going—</font>

105
00:06:13,650 --> 00:06:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A boy?</i></font>

106
00:06:15,980 --> 00:06:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it's already dark. 
When did he get here?</i></font>

107
00:06:19,310 --> 00:06:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you here by yourself?</font>

108
00:06:23,860 --> 00:06:25,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are your parents?</font>

109
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't be out alone this late.</font>

110
00:06:28,130 --> 00:06:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I teach at the kindergarten nearby.</font>

111
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If something's bothering you, 
we can talk there—</font>

112
00:06:43,220 --> 00:06:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

113
00:06:44,990 --> 00:06:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toshi-chan!</font>

114
00:06:47,570 --> 00:06:49,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toshi-chan!</font>

115
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mommy!</font>

116
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Is my son bothering you?</font>

117
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no, it's not like that. 
I'm sorry to surprise you.</font>

118
00:06:54,130 --> 00:06:56,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mommy!</font>

119
00:06:58,350 --> 00:07:02,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How embarrassing. I didn't notice them
 because I was glued to my phone.</i></font>

120
00:06:58,350 --> 00:07:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mommy!</font>

121
00:07:02,540 --> 00:07:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mommy!</font>

122
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to scare you—</font>

123
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mommy!</font>

124
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:11,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mommy!</font>

125
00:07:10,410 --> 00:07:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's this weird feeling I'm getting? 
Something's off.</i></font>

126
00:07:11,910 --> 00:07:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Toshi-chan!</font>

127
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:15,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mommy!</font>

128
00:07:14,950 --> 00:07:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When someone died...</i></font>

129
00:07:15,410 --> 00:07:17,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Toshi-chan!</font>

130
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...everything got reversed.</i></font>

131
00:07:18,990 --> 00:07:21,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Toshi-chan!</font>

132
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Toshi-chan!</font>

133
00:07:31,810 --> 00:07:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Th-This isn't good!</i></font>

134
00:07:34,340 --> 00:07:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something bad's gonna happen 
if I stay here!</i></font>

135
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:40,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry.</font>

136
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:42,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chie-sensei?</font>

137
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

138
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mob-san!</font>

139
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:49,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?</font>

140
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's my line. <i>You're</i> the one 
who told me to come here!</font>

141
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But never mind that. 
This place isn't safe. We need to go.</font>

142
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a ghost mother and child over—</font>

143
00:08:01,470 --> 00:08:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A ghost mother and child? Ooh, intriguing!</font>

144
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:06,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gimme the details.</font>

145
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't chat here! 
Everything's reversed!</font>

146
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know about it, right, Mob-san?</font>

147
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How everything's reversed 
for dead people—</font>

148
00:08:16,350 --> 00:08:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font color="#140019">tsohG</font></font></font>

149
00:08:18,350 --> 00:08:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="52"><font color="#140019">tsohG</font></font></font>

150
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, so you're familiar 
with the "reversed" custom?</font>

151
00:08:24,230 --> 00:08:28,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure know your stuff, Chie-sensei.</font>

152
00:08:30,110 --> 00:08:34,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, no. My legs gave out.</i></font>

153
00:08:30,110 --> 00:08:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Clap, clap, clap. Clap, clap, clap.</font>

154
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Clap, clap, clap. Clap, clap, clap.</font>

155
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you are.</font>

156
00:08:42,970 --> 00:08:46,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, is he dead? Uh...</font>

157
00:08:47,710 --> 00:08:50,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon, Osamu-kun. Wake up.</font>

158
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone'll call the cops 
on you again if you sleep here.</font>

159
00:08:57,090 --> 00:08:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, <i>that's</i> what I call refreshing!</font>

160
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel so light! 
As if a curse has been lifted.</font>

161
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:04,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yeah. That's what happened.</font>

162
00:09:04,300 --> 00:09:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

163
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

164
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you doing here...</font>

165
00:09:09,610 --> 00:09:11,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">m-m-master?!</font>

166
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A <i>d-decoy</i>?!</font>

167
00:09:16,290 --> 00:09:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. You found Chie-sensei 
in my call history,</font>

168
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and brought her to a place 
where specters were likely to appear.</font>

169
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:24,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

170
00:09:24,810 --> 00:09:26,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive, master.</font>

171
00:09:26,300 --> 00:09:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say what?!</font>

172
00:09:28,300 --> 00:09:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you're okay, Osamu-kun.</font>

173
00:09:30,950 --> 00:09:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for looking after me.</font>

174
00:09:33,090 --> 00:09:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't move on without me.</font>

175
00:09:35,930 --> 00:09:39,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a million questions, 
but first, who are <i>you</i> supposed to be?</font>

176
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Loom.</font>

177
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My master isn't good with people.</font>

178
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? And what's all that "master" stuff?</font>

179
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His name is Namu-san.</font>

180
00:09:49,110 --> 00:09:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gained my knowledge
 of spirits from him.</font>

181
00:09:53,610 --> 00:09:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Namu-san?</font>

182
00:09:55,790 --> 00:10:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a great psychic whose powers are 
so strong, he can't settle in one place.</font>

183
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he's suspicious person number two,
 and he's homeless and without a job.</font>

184
00:10:08,510 --> 00:10:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a little mercy.</font>

185
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't matter.</font>

186
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

187
00:10:13,380 --> 00:10:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is our last time 
speaking to each other.</font>

188
00:10:15,890 --> 00:10:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I warned you, didn't I, Osamu-kun?</font>

189
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About not getting involved 
with the Ebisumori shrine maiden.</font>

190
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ebisumori?</i></font>

191
00:10:25,020 --> 00:10:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got lucky this time 
that it was only a minor possession.</font>

192
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oopsie-daisy.</font>

193
00:10:29,390 --> 00:10:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might not be so simple the next time—</font>

194
00:10:31,420 --> 00:10:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it right there.</font>

195
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He just said "Ebisumori."</i></font>

196
00:10:36,350 --> 00:10:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's Kaya-chan's mother's maiden name,</i></font>

197
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and the last name of the psychic granny 
and the aunt who showed up out of nowhere.</i></font>

198
00:10:42,270 --> 00:10:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this about the Ebisumori family?</font>

199
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean? You got involved 
not knowing who they are?</font>

200
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No wonder you panicked earlier.</font>

201
00:10:52,940 --> 00:10:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that family,</font>

202
00:10:54,550 --> 00:10:59,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the eldest Ebisumori daughter inherits
power beyond the ordinary for generations.</font>

203
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The eldest daughter?</font>

204
00:11:02,570 --> 00:11:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That little one is 
the eldest, too, isn't she?</font>

205
00:11:05,410 --> 00:11:09,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even so, that one's on 
a whole other level. A monster.</font>

206
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:12,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because Osamu-kun is 
too perceptive for his own good,</font>

207
00:11:12,990 --> 00:11:15,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he seems to attract 
all kinds of spirits now.</font>

208
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:19,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wasn't that thing 
supposed to be locked up?</font>

209
00:11:19,700 --> 00:11:22,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They can't just set 
something like that loose.</font>

210
00:11:22,710 --> 00:11:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck is 
that old Ebisumori woman doing?</font>

211
00:11:25,290 --> 00:11:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Actually, Mutsu-san is...</font>

212
00:11:27,100 --> 00:11:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait a second!</font>

213
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, Kaya-chan does indeed 
possess mysterious powers.</font>

214
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she's not a monster.</font>

215
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's an ordinary girl 
you'd find anywhere.</font>

216
00:11:38,180 --> 00:11:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't say such awful things!</font>

217
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Individual good or evil means nothing 
in the face of such overwhelming power.</font>

218
00:11:46,430 --> 00:11:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet you know what I'm talking about.</font>

219
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

220
00:11:56,950 --> 00:12:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Kaya-chan
<font size="22">\h\h\hIsn't</font></font></b></font></font></font>

221
00:11:56,950 --> 00:12:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Scary</font></b></font></font></font>

222
00:12:02,950 --> 00:12:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Kaya-chan
<font size="22">\h\h\hIsn't</font></font></b></font></font></font>

223
00:12:02,950 --> 00:12:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Scary</font></b></font></font></font>

224
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">The Sandbox Isn't Scary</font></b></font></font>

225
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

226
00:12:21,100 --> 00:12:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hi, Kaya-chan.</font>

227
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you going to make?</font>

228
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A mountain.</font>

229
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope! That's not how you do it!</font>

230
00:12:30,970 --> 00:12:31,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

231
00:12:31,810 --> 00:12:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a job site run by my company, 
Nakahashi Construction.</font>

232
00:12:36,420 --> 00:12:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't join us if you're not
 gonna take it seriously.</font>

233
00:12:39,890 --> 00:12:42,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You heard him!
Listen to what our boss says!</font>

234
00:12:42,450 --> 00:12:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, <i>this</i> won't cut it. All you 
did was pile up sand and that's it.</font>

235
00:12:46,880 --> 00:12:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gotta pat it down 
like this with the shovel.</font>

236
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hear that? That's the sound you want.</font>

237
00:12:53,540 --> 00:12:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See?</font>

238
00:12:55,340 --> 00:12:57,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excellent work, boss.</font>

239
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boss!</font>

240
00:12:58,310 --> 00:13:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it? Now you try.</font>

241
00:13:10,850 --> 00:13:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?!</font>

242
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're fired! Fired, fired, fired!</font>

243
00:13:23,370 --> 00:13:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut her some slack, boss. 
Kaya-chan wants to join you.</font>

244
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:29,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, she can't!</font>

245
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'll just mess up what I made again!</font>

246
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it!</font>

247
00:13:38,580 --> 00:13:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

248
00:13:40,190 --> 00:13:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

249
00:13:41,510 --> 00:13:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your mountain's so cool, Ma-kun.</font>

250
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's the tunnel, 
and this is the hiking trail.</font>

251
00:13:47,290 --> 00:13:49,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like a real mountain!</font>

252
00:13:49,350 --> 00:13:51,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so fussy, Masaru.</font>

253
00:13:51,350 --> 00:13:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's called being skilled.</font>

254
00:13:52,770 --> 00:13:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're number one at making mountains,
 Ma-kun. You're so cool!</font>

255
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph, that's nothin'.</font>

256
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

257
00:14:00,330 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine's bigger.</font>

258
00:14:02,900 --> 00:14:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll just add a tunnel now.</font>

259
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The boss is jealous.</font>

260
00:14:07,020 --> 00:14:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He hates to lose.</font>

261
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't just watch. Gimme a hand!</font>

262
00:14:11,830 --> 00:14:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah. This one's more fun to watch.</font>

263
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

264
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:21,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is someone digging 
from the other side, too?</i></font>

265
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But who? The mountain's 
too tall for me to see who it is.</i></font>

266
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, whatever. Who cares?</i></font>

267
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a little more. Keep digging.</font>

268
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:34,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost there!</font>

269
00:14:37,020 --> 00:14:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so cold! Don't grab me like that.
 You freaked me out.</font>

270
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:45,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, whatever. The tunnel's complete!</font>

271
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck? I can't get up 
if you're holding my hand!</font>

272
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:50,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let go!</font>

273
00:14:52,330 --> 00:14:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doin'? You're too strong.</font>

274
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, boss.</font>

275
00:14:56,790 --> 00:15:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop being so stubborn and come join us.</font>

276
00:15:00,100 --> 00:15:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up! The person on 
the other side won't let go of me.</font>

277
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

278
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about? 
You're the only one digging the tunnel.</font>

279
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

280
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck? Stop!</font>

281
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:21,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let go of me! Hey, what are you doin'?</font>

282
00:15:21,570 --> 00:15:23,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop pullin' my arm!</font>

283
00:15:23,330 --> 00:15:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck?! Who are you?!</font>

284
00:15:37,510 --> 00:15:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

285
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-oh, Kaya-chan. You shouldn't ruin
 someone else's mountain.</font>

286
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:46,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do anything to mine, okay?</font>

287
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll get in trouble for swinging 
a shovel around, too.</font>

288
00:15:49,390 --> 00:15:53,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It felt like something 
was inside the tunnel.</i></font>

289
00:15:49,930 --> 00:15:51,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}He's right, you know.</font>

290
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:56,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No way. It was just my imagination.</i></font>

291
00:16:02,970 --> 00:16:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan!</font>

292
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

293
00:16:05,940 --> 00:16:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's make sand balls together.</font>

294
00:16:08,740 --> 00:16:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming.</font>

295
00:16:10,370 --> 00:16:10,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

296
00:16:14,700 --> 00:16:17,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up, Kaya-chan.</font>

297
00:16:17,330 --> 00:16:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

298
00:16:24,210 --> 00:16:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you explain this?!</font>

299
00:16:26,260 --> 00:16:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did he get this bruise on his arm?</font>

300
00:16:28,530 --> 00:16:31,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should've kept a closer eye
 on him. We're very sorry.</font>

301
00:16:32,690 --> 00:16:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really don't know who did it to you?</font>

302
00:16:36,310 --> 00:16:38,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There was nobody around you?</font>

303
00:16:39,860 --> 00:16:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan was.</font>

304
00:16:43,170 --> 00:16:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

305
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She beat it up for me, so...</font>

306
00:16:48,530 --> 00:16:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beat up who?</font>

307
00:16:51,160 --> 00:16:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The g-ghost.</font>

308
00:16:56,330 --> 00:17:00,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="36">{\an9}<font color="#554f4a">Staff Room</font></font></font></font>

309
00:16:56,330 --> 00:17:00,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We never found out 
how he got that bruise on his arm.</font>

310
00:17:00,830 --> 00:17:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure Nakahashi-san isn't satisfied.</font>

311
00:17:04,660 --> 00:17:08,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is what it is. We have to do a good job
 going forward to rebuild their trust.</font>

312
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font color="#1f1e1d">Injury Log</font></font></b></font>

313
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an7}<font size="10"><font color="#1f1e1d">Tamura Asuka — Playground
<font size="8">Collided head-on during tag and got a nosebleed.
Applied ice to stop the bleeding.</font></font></font></b></font>

314
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an7}<font size="10"><font color="#1f1e1d">Sakurai Rihito — Same as above
<font size="8"> Bump on forehead. Applied ice.</font></font></font></b></font>

315
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an7}<font size="10"><font color="#1f1e1d">Nakahashi Yuki — Sandbox
<font size="8"> Unexplained bruise on right arm. Applied ice.</font></font></font></b></font>

316
00:17:09,360 --> 00:17:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, a ghost? That sounds like 
something Kaya-chan would say.</font>

317
00:17:14,260 --> 00:17:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it the in thing now or something?</font>

318
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Know anything, Chie-sensei?</font>

319
00:17:19,270 --> 00:17:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

320
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That one's on a whole 
other level. A monster.</font>

321
00:17:26,990 --> 00:17:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">K-Kaya-chan isn't a ghost!</font>

322
00:17:31,470 --> 00:17:33,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, c'mon. What are you even saying?</font>

323
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course she's not. 
That's not what we're saying.</font>

324
00:17:37,490 --> 00:17:40,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, of course.</font>

325
00:17:41,430 --> 00:17:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

326
00:17:46,210 --> 00:17:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Nice People Aren't Scary?</font></b></font></font>

327
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font face="Georgia"><font size="30"><font color="#faf8ee">Family Fall Festival</font></font></font></b></font>

328
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's time for our annual 
Family Fall Festival.</i></font>

329
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:55,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let the fun begin!</i></font>

330
00:17:57,680 --> 00:18:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trick or treat!</font>

331
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:00,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

332
00:18:00,970 --> 00:18:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

333
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And one for you.</font>

334
00:18:03,690 --> 00:18:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thankin' ya!</font>

335
00:18:05,210 --> 00:18:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's the teachers 
from Hanamugi. Sensei!</font>

336
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long time no see, Akira-sensei.
You're dressed as a demon?</font>

337
00:18:12,950 --> 00:18:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, look at you! 
Getting bigger every year.</font>

338
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was sulking about giving up our day off
 for community service, but...</font>

339
00:18:20,060 --> 00:18:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't complain after seeing that.</font>

340
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei! Trick or treat!</font>

341
00:18:26,330 --> 00:18:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being an experienced teacher
 has its upsides.</font>

342
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess so.</font>

343
00:18:30,990 --> 00:18:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

344
00:18:32,650 --> 00:18:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait. Just now...</i></font>

345
00:18:35,180 --> 00:18:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could've sworn I saw someone
 who didn't fit in.</i></font>

346
00:18:39,790 --> 00:18:42,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up, Chie-sensei?</font>

347
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:44,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, nothing.</font>

348
00:18:44,150 --> 00:18:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

349
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trick or treat!</font>

350
00:18:47,380 --> 00:18:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boo!</font>

351
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:49,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan!</font>

352
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi.</font>

353
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:54,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello. Here with your dad today?</font>

354
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

355
00:18:55,530 --> 00:18:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been at the hospital 
with my wife most weekends.</font>

356
00:18:59,870 --> 00:19:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How is Kaya-chan's mother doing?</font>

357
00:19:03,460 --> 00:19:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's doing a lot better.</font>

358
00:19:05,220 --> 00:19:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's great.</font>

359
00:19:07,040 --> 00:19:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate all the help 
the kindergarten gives us.</font>

360
00:19:10,100 --> 00:19:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's nothing.</font>

361
00:19:13,140 --> 00:19:15,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daddy, I wanna do that raffle.</font>

362
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

363
00:19:16,930 --> 00:19:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Da—</font>

364
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what's the matter?</font>

365
00:19:20,230 --> 00:19:23,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, did you mistake me for your daddy?</font>

366
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:40,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Daddy!</font>

367
00:19:41,490 --> 00:19:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm? Oh, you're that girl from earlier.</font>

368
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:46,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you're really lost, huh?</font>

369
00:19:48,420 --> 00:19:51,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're in trouble, right? I'll help you.</font>

370
00:19:53,050 --> 00:19:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

371
00:20:03,510 --> 00:20:04,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See?</font>

372
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:08,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came to me again.</font>

373
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet you actually want to play 
with me. Isn't that right?</font>

374
00:20:22,450 --> 00:20:26,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a naughty girl. 
You shouldn't hit people.</font>

375
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No!</font>

376
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

377
00:20:32,460 --> 00:20:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help me! I wanna go home!</font>

378
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lemme go!</font>

379
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Calm down. These ghosts aren't real.</font>

380
00:20:39,710 --> 00:20:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna go home!</font>

381
00:20:40,820 --> 00:20:42,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna go home!</font>

382
00:20:40,820 --> 00:20:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's okay.</font>

383
00:20:42,430 --> 00:20:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh, I see. She's still little. 
Must be rough on her father.</font>

384
00:20:44,810 --> 00:20:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let go!</font>

385
00:20:47,040 --> 00:20:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}How cute.</font>

386
00:20:48,430 --> 00:20:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's go get some treats together.</font>

387
00:20:51,950 --> 00:20:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want any! Let go!</font>

388
00:20:57,560 --> 00:20:58,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just come with me.</font>

389
00:20:59,500 --> 00:21:02,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't like monsters, do you?</font>

390
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be good and nothing scary will happen.</font>

391
00:21:06,900 --> 00:21:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... Why?</font>

392
00:21:11,620 --> 00:21:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm strong.</font>

393
00:21:14,100 --> 00:21:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why can't I... How come?</font>

394
00:21:16,840 --> 00:21:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm...</font>

395
00:21:19,170 --> 00:21:19,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

396
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has my daughter done something?</font>

397
00:21:22,850 --> 00:21:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are they arguing?</font>

398
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:25,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, he's <i>not</i> her father?</font>

399
00:21:25,930 --> 00:21:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yuck. He's just some perv?</font>

400
00:21:28,060 --> 00:21:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you let go of her now?</font>

401
00:21:31,270 --> 00:21:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's the one who was following <i>me</i>!</font>

402
00:21:33,810 --> 00:21:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should watch your kid 
if you're a parent.</font>

403
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:38,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever, man.</font>

404
00:21:41,850 --> 00:21:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your powers don't work 
on normal human beings.</font>

405
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but you wouldn't 
understand what I'm...</font>

406
00:21:54,810 --> 00:21:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's no use.</font>

407
00:22:01,710 --> 00:22:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is exactly why monsters 
can't live among humans.</font>

408
00:22:15,270 --> 00:22:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<b><font size="10">Translation
Timing
Editing
Quality Control
Translation Check</font></b></font>

409
